{"tid":2208460,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個廚房佬幾屈機","createTime":"2020-09-19T02:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T06:11:08.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"029e2671e71ed7c63a9798b35e837ad7d17ccea4","tid":2208460,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F5z1gmMBoxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF5z1gmMBoxg&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=39daefb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F5z1gmMBoxg</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完條片想去佢間店試下<br />\n然後下面又有人屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n利苑 2000年前就係香港飲食指標 今時今日同普通酒樓無咩分別 另外做利苑只要扮傻仔返工 日日比人罵 3-5年左右 就可以做所謂大廚 做得飲食業耐都知道 十個有7個都係呃飯食 每個都吹到自己有幾勁 做過幾多間廚房大佬 咁又如何呀 真正有料有廚藝嘅師傅 仲有幾多個吖 真心希望香港廚師們 努力為我們的手藝 堅持落去<br />\n<br />\n見渠個青椒料頭飛水就知咩料啦，雞湯蝦湯你用新鮮呃鬼咩，呃下啲扮食家就得，00年到15年系利苑 最垃圾時候，仲好意思講出來"},{"pid":"bf972d8a300f99f410798b28d9205aac86bd7d2e","tid":2208460,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"得個名煮鳩菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec9f5a17612f7817f7513c7ebcfb94fd99bb6fd","tid":2208460,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf972d8a300f99f410798b28d9205aac86bd7d2e","tid":2208460,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"得個名煮鳩菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得蘋果真係專門吹奏呢類人"},{"pid":"f86aa08e38e217acb01eb0fcb0704d8859888010","tid":2208460,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faede8047583f7d12c843c82a843aff8d02fbaf2","tid":2208460,"uid":80426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"每次行過呢間野 成個門口都係地盤佬同煙鏟 係門口，見到都唔想入去食。"}]}